#ROOM
Vnum     21600
Name     &xThe Gates of Caer Darrow&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The high stone walls of the Barov family manor tower overhead. 
A massive iron gate, rusted but immovable, blocks the way to the 
island's inner keep. A shimmering, dark blue portal glows within 
the archway, leading into the Academy of Necromancy. The air 
is absolute still, and the sky is a permanent, bruised purple.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    38080
Desc      Return to the ruins of Caer Darrow.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21601
Desc      The Entry Hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21601
Name     &xThe Entry Hall of Scholomance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A grand hall with high, vaulted ceilings. Shattered marble 
statues of the Barov ancestors line the walls, and the floor 
is covered in a thick layer of dust. Spectral chamberlains 
hurry through the shadows, ignoring your presence.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21600
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21602
Desc      The Grand Crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21538 1 21601
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21602
Name     &xThe Grand Crossroads&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The main hallway of the academy splits here. To the east lies 
the Reliquary, while to the west, a wide ramp leads down 
into the Great Ossuary. To the north, the sounds of shouting 
and clanking armor suggest the military quarters.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21601
Desc      The entry hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21603
Desc      Toward the Reliquary.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21615
Desc      Toward the Great Ossuary.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21630
Desc      Toward the Dungeons.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21511 10 21602
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21603
Name     &xThe Reliquary - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A long, narrow hallway filled with glass display cases. Inside 
are the shriveled remains of saints and kings, now used as 
arcane batteries for the academy's research.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21602
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21604
Desc      Deep into the Reliquary.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21517 5 21603
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21604
Name     &xThe Reliquary - Central Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide intersection where several wings of the Reliquary meet. 
High-level specters strike from the rafters, their wails 
echoing through the stone like a physical blow.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21603
Desc      The reliquary entry.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21605
Desc      The Herald's Balcony.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21606
Desc      Toward the Blood-Pit.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21536 10 21604
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21605
Name     &xThe Herald's Balcony&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone balcony overlooking the lake. A large stone 
altar is used to summon Kirtonos the Herald. The air 
smells of fresh blood and ozone.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21604
Desc      The central hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21504 1 21605
  Reset G 1 21544 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21606
Name     &xThe Blood-Pit - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls here are stained with a permanent layer of dried 
gore. The sound of wet squelching comes from the cavern 
ahead, along with the giggles of Doctor Krastinov.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21604
Desc      The central hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21607
Desc      Krastinov's Lab.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21524 5 21606
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21607
Name     &xThe Lab of Doctor Krastinov&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A scene of absolute carnage. Dissected bodies are stacked in 
piles, and several large tables are covered in jagged surgical 
tools. Doctor Krastinov stands here, his hands dripping 
with blood as he prepares a new subject.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21606
Desc      The pit entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21505 1 21607
  Reset E 1 21548 1 16
  Reset G 1 21573 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21608
Name     &xReliquary Overflow A&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small side chamber filled with jars of ectoplasmic residue 
and shriveled fingers.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21603
Desc      Reliquary entry.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 21568 10 21608
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21609
Name     &xReliquary Overflow B&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone landing near the Herald's balcony, frequently 
patrolled by spectral tutors.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21604
Desc      Reliquary central.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21513 5 21609
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21610
Name     &xThe Butchery Side-room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A dark room near Krastinov's lab where the reanimated 
corpses are stored before being processed.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21607
Desc      Krastinov's lab.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21514 10 21610
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21615
Name     &xThe Great Ossuary - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide stone ramp descending into a massive subterranean 
chamber. The air is cold and smells of ancient bone-dust. 
Piles of bleached skulls line the path.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21602
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21616
Desc      The Bone-Pit Floor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21535 10 21615
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21616
Name     &xThe Bone-Pit Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The floor of the ossuary is covered in a five-foot deep pile 
of assorted humanoid bones. Rattlegore stands in the center, 
his massive frame towering over the heaps of bleached 
remains.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21615
Desc      The entrance ramp.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21617
Desc      Toward the Crypt of the Barovs.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21622
Desc      Toward the Alchemy Lab.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21502 1 21616
  Reset G 1 21564 1
  Reset G 1 21546 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21617
Name     &xThe Crypt of the Barovs - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls here are decorated with the family crest of the 
Barovs. Stone sarcophagi are built into the mountain 
side, their lids long ago pried open by the Scourge.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21616
Desc      The bone-pit floor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21618
Desc      Deep into the Crypt.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21508 1 21617
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21618
Name     &xThe Crypt of the Barovs - Inner Vault&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest-ranking members of the family are interred here. 
Lord Alexei Barov stands in silent vigil, his spectral 
armor reflecting the cold light of the room.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21617
Desc      The crypt entry.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21509 1 21618
  Reset G 1 21542 1
  Reset G 1 21575 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21619
Name     &xThe Shadowed Crypt&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     A small, isolated crypt used for the family's distant 
relatives. It is now infested with crypt stalkers.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21617
Desc      The crypt entry.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21522 10 21619
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21620
Name     &xOssuary Overflow A&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A quiet section of the bone-pit where the marrow 
has been extracted for magical fuel.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21616
Desc      The bone-pit floor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21535 5 21620
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21621
Name     &xOssuary Overflow B&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone landing near the ossuary ceiling, 
home to several large plaguehounds.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    21616
Desc      The bone-pit floor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21518 5 21621
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21622
Name     &xThe Road to the Lab - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A hallway lined with cold iron pillars. The air becomes 
noticeably more chemical and bitter as you approach 
the alchemy district.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21616
Desc      The bone-pit.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21623
Desc      The Alchemy Lab Entry.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21511 5 21622
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21623
Name     &xThe Alchemy Lab - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large room filled with workbenches, beakers, and bubbling 
cauldrons. Lab assistants move mindlessly, following the 
orders of the master lich.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21622
Desc      The road to the lab.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21624
Desc      Ras Frostwhisper's Lab.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21525 10 21623
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21624
Name     &xThe Lab of Ras Frostwhisper&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The entire room is coated in a permanent layer of thick 
blue frost. Ras Frostwhisper floats in the center, 
his power keeping the reagents from spoiling. Arcane 
energies pulse from his staff, shaking the floor.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21623
Desc      The lab entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 21501 1 21624
  Reset G 1 21545 1
  Reset G 1 21570 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21625
Name     &xLab Overflow A&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A side storage room filled with crates of plaguebloom 
and bottles of frozen ichor.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21623
Desc      The lab entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 21552 10 21625
#ENDROOM

