Vnum     21630
Name     &xThe Dungeons - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A steep set of stairs leads down into the heart of the 
mountain. The walls are damp and the air reeks of 
Hopelessness and old rot. The sound of chains 
clanking is constant.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21602
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    21631
