Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide intersection where several dungeon wings meet. 
The Ravenian can be seen feasting on a pile of 
refuse in the center of the hall.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    21630
Desc      The entrance stairs.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21632
Desc      Toward the Summoning Rooms.~
