Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A series of high-domed rooms where the academy teaches 
the art of spirit-manifestation. The air here is thin 
and hums with a permanent spectral pitch.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    21631
Desc      The detention hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    21633
Desc      Jandice Barov's Hall.~
