#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     21641
Name     &rThe Throne of Darkmaster Gandling&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of Scholomance. Darkmaster Gandling sits 
upon a throne of bone and shadow, his eyes glowing with 
